title: [FSX/P3D] Flysimware - Mitsubishi MU-2B-60 v1.8
description:
Flysimware - Mitsubishi MU-2B-60 v1.8
Custom quad installer for FSX/FSX:SE/P3Dv2/P3Dv3

Rev 1.8 (OCT 10, 2015)
What is new in update?

Lights now work from key commands
Prop blur effect updated
User manual now shows avionics switch location
Rudder and elevator trim tab animation updated
Ground power unit added to model
All lights now have a battery load and we included other system loads
Annunciator texture updated
DC and AC meters updated
P3D V3 installer

Note: 
     The software that I upload to TPB is not my work.
     I find it elsewhere on the internet and share it here with you guys.
     I cannot take credit for the Hard work that others have done.
     Credit to the People who do the cracking.

     NoFlyZone

Enjoy and please seed
